Simple "Tag-Cloud"-like html output of your completely watched anime. It creates an alphabetically ordered list with the font-size of the title corresponding to your permanent vote.

no permanent vote:    font size 1
1 <= your vote <= 4:  font size 1
4 <  your vote <= 5:  font size 2
5 <  your vote <= 6:  font size 3
6 <  your vote <= 7:  font size 4
7 <  your vote <= 8:  font size 5
8 <  your vote <= 9:  font size 6
9 <  your vote <= 10: font size 7
